sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (Any Role)
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant DB as Database
    participant GEMINI as Gemini AI API
    participant CONTEXT as Context Builder

    Note over U,CONTEXT: TENANT CHATBOT FLOW

    Note over U,CONTEXT: Initialize Chatbot Session

    U->>FE: Click floating chatbot button
    Note right of U: Button visible on all pages<br/>Shows: 💬 icon
    
    FE->>FE: Open chatbot modal
    Note right of FE: Modal appearance:<br/>- Width: 400px<br/>- Height: 600px<br/>- Position: bottom-right<br/>- Animation: slide-up
    
    FE->>DB: Query user profile + context
    Note right of DB: SELECT<br/>  user role,<br/>  tenant/merchant/vendor data,<br/>  property details,<br/>  active contracts,<br/>  recent activity,<br/>  open issues
    
    DB-->>FE: Return user context
    
    FE->>U: Display chatbot interface
    Note right of U: UI components:<br/><br/>🤖 Header<br/>- "SiHuni Assistant"<br/>- "Always here to help"<br/>- Minimize/close buttons<br/><br/>💬 Chat Area<br/>- Message bubbles<br/>- Typing indicator<br/>- Timestamps<br/><br/>📝 Input Box<br/>- Text input<br/>- Send button<br/>- Voice input (optional)<br/><br/>💡 Quick Actions<br/>- Suggested questions<br/>- Common tasks
    
    FE->>U: Show welcome message
    Note right of U: "Hi [Name]! 👋<br/>I'm your SiHuni assistant.<br/>How can I help you today?"
    
    FE->>U: Display quick action buttons
    Note right of U: For Tenant:<br/>🏠 "Check my rent status"<br/>💰 "View upcoming payments"<br/>🔧 "Report maintenance issue"<br/>🛒 "Find nearby laundry service"<br/>❓ "Help with something else"
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: User Asks Question (FAQ Type)

    U->>FE: Type question
    Note right of U: "Cara bayar sewa gimana?"<br/>(How do I pay rent?)
    
    FE->>FE: Add user message to chat
    FE->>FE: Show typing indicator
    
    FE->>CONTEXT: Build conversation context
    
    CONTEXT->>DB: Query relevant data
    Note right of DB: For Tenant FAQ:<br/>- Tenant profile<br/>- Active invoice status<br/>- Payment history<br/>- Property details<br/>- Merchant info
    
    DB-->>CONTEXT: Return contextual data
    
    CONTEXT->>CONTEXT: Build system prompt
    Note right of CONTEXT: System prompt structure:<br/><br/>"You are SiHuni Assistant for Tenant.<br/><br/>User context:<br/>- Name: [Name]<br/>- Property: [Property Name]<br/>- Unit: [Unit Number]<br/>- Active contract: Yes/No<br/>- Unpaid invoices: [Count]<br/>- Last payment: [Date]<br/><br/>Guidelines:<br/>- Answer in Bahasa Indonesia<br/>- Be friendly and helpful<br/>- Provide step-by-step instructions<br/>- Include relevant links when possible<br/>- If asking for personal data, explain why<br/><br/>Available actions you can suggest:<br/>- View invoices: /tenant/invoices<br/>- Make payment: [direct link]<br/>- Contact support: support@sihuni.com"
    
    CONTEXT->>CONTEXT: Prepare message history
    Note right of CONTEXT: Format:<br/>[<br/>  {role: "user", content: "Cara bayar sewa?"},<br/>  // Previous messages if any<br/>]
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: POST to Gemini API
    Note right of GEMINI: API Request:<br/>{<br/>  model: "gemini-2.0-flash-exp",<br/>  systemInstruction: system_prompt,<br/>  contents: message_history<br/>}
    
    GEMINI->>GEMINI: Process query with context
    Note right of GEMINI: Gemini understands:<br/>- User is a tenant<br/>- Question is about payment<br/>- User has Indonesian preference<br/>- Context: Has active contract
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Return AI response
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Untuk bayar sewa, ikuti langkah ini:<br/><br/>1. Buka halaman 'Tagihan Saya'<br/>2. Pilih invoice yang ingin dibayar<br/>3. Pilih metode pembayaran:<br/>   - Virtual Account (BCA, BNI, dll)<br/>   - QRIS<br/>   - E-Wallet<br/>   - Kartu Kredit<br/>4. Selesaikan pembayaran<br/>5. Bukti akan dikirim ke email<br/><br/>Kamu punya 1 tagihan belum dibayar:<br/>- Rp 1,500,000 (jatuh tempo: 27 Des)<br/><br/>[Bayar Sekarang]"
    
    CONTEXT->>FE: Return formatted response
    
    FE->>FE: Parse response for actions
    Note right of FE: Detect action buttons:<br/>- [Bayar Sekarang] → Link to invoice<br/>- Convert markdown to HTML<br/>- Format numbered lists
    
    FE->>U: Display AI response with actions
    Note right of U: Shows:<br/>- AI message bubble (left)<br/>- Formatted text<br/>- Clickable action button<br/>- Timestamp
    
    FE->>DB: Log conversation
    Note right of DB: INSERT INTO chatbot_conversations<br/>user_id, role,<br/>user_message, ai_response,<br/>context_used, timestamp
    
    U->>FE: Click "Bayar Sekarang" button
    FE->>U: Navigate to /tenant/invoices/{id}
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: Complex Query (Data-Driven)

    U->>FE: Ask complex question
    Note right of U: "Rekomendasi laundry terdekat<br/>dengan rating bagus dong"
    
    FE->>CONTEXT: Build context with data access
    
    CONTEXT->>DB: Query vendor data
    Note right of DB: SELECT * FROM vendors<br/>WHERE category = 'Laundry'<br/>AND verified = true<br/>AND avg_rating >= 4.0<br/>ORDER BY<br/>  DISTANCE(vendor_location, user_property)<br/>LIMIT 5
    
    DB-->>CONTEXT: Return vendor list
    Note right of CONTEXT: Results:<br/>1. LaundryKu - 4.8★ - 500m<br/>2. Clean Express - 4.7★ - 800m<br/>3. Wash & Go - 4.5★ - 1.2km
    
    CONTEXT->>CONTEXT: Build enriched prompt
    Note right of CONTEXT: System prompt + Data:<br/>"User is looking for laundry services.<br/><br/>Available vendors near user:<br/>1. LaundryKu<br/>   - Rating: 4.8/5 (120 reviews)<br/>   - Distance: 500m<br/>   - Price: Rp 8k/kg<br/>   - Operating: 08:00-20:00<br/><br/>2. Clean Express<br/>   - Rating: 4.7/5 (85 reviews)<br/>   - Distance: 800m<br/>   - Price: Rp 7k/kg<br/><br/>3. Wash & Go<br/>   - Rating: 4.5/5 (95 reviews)<br/>   - Distance: 1.2km<br/>   - Price: Rp 6.5k/kg<br/><br/>Provide personalized recommendation."
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: Send enriched request
    
    GEMINI->>GEMINI: Analyze & recommend
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Return recommendation
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Berikut rekomendasi laundry terdekat:<br/><br/>🏆 Paling Direkomendasikan:<br/>LaundryKu ⭐ 4.8<br/>- Jarak: 500m (jalan kaki 6 menit)<br/>- Harga: Rp 8,000/kg<br/>- Buka: 08:00-20:00<br/>- Review: 'Cepat & bersih!'<br/>[Lihat Detail] [Pesan Sekarang]<br/><br/>Alternatif lain:<br/>✓ Clean Express (800m) - 4.7★<br/>✓ Wash & Go (1.2km) - 4.5★<br/><br/>Mau pesan sekarang?"
    
    FE->>U: Display recommendations with actions
    
    U->>FE: Click "Pesan Sekarang"
    FE->>U: Navigate to vendor profile + pre-fill order
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: MERCHANT CHATBOT FLOW

    Note over U,CONTEXT: Merchant Business Query

    U->>FE: Open merchant chatbot
    Note right of U: User role: Merchant
    
    FE->>DB: Query merchant business data
    Note right of DB: Context for Merchant:<br/>- Properties count<br/>- Total tenants<br/>- Unpaid invoices list<br/>- Recent payments<br/>- Occupancy rate<br/>- Revenue metrics<br/>- Pending maintenance
    
    DB-->>CONTEXT: Return business context
    
    U->>FE: Ask business question
    Note right of U: "Tenant mana yang belum bayar<br/>bulan ini?"
    
    CONTEXT->>CONTEXT: Build merchant prompt with data
    Note right of CONTEXT: System prompt:<br/>"You are business assistant for Merchant.<br/><br/>Current business data:<br/>- Total tenants: 25<br/>- Paid this month: 18<br/>- Unpaid this month: 7<br/>- Total revenue: Rp 37,500,000<br/>- Occupancy: 92%<br/><br/>Unpaid tenants:<br/>1. John Doe - Unit 203 - Rp 1.5M<br/>   Due: 2 days overdue<br/>2. Jane Smith - Unit 105 - Rp 1.8M<br/>   Due: Today<br/>3. [... 5 more]<br/><br/>Provide clear summary and suggest actions."
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: Send request
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Return analysis
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Ada 7 tenant yang belum bayar:<br/><br/>⚠️ Perlu Tindakan Segera:<br/>1. John Doe (Unit 203)<br/>   Rp 1,500,000 - Terlambat 2 hari<br/>   [Kirim Reminder] [Lihat Detail]<br/><br/>2. Jane Smith (Unit 105)<br/>   Rp 1,800,000 - Jatuh tempo hari ini<br/>   [Kirim Reminder]<br/><br/>📊 Total belum terbayar: Rp 10.2 juta<br/><br/>💡 Saran:<br/>- Kirim reminder otomatis ke semua<br/>- Follow up personal untuk terlambat 2+ hari<br/><br/>[Kirim Reminder ke Semua]<br/>[Lihat Laporan Lengkap]"
    
    FE->>U: Display actionable insights
    
    U->>FE: Click "Kirim Reminder ke Semua"
    FE->>DB: Trigger bulk reminder emails
    
    DB-->>U: Success: "7 reminders sent"
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: Predictive Analytics Query

    U->>FE: Ask prediction question
    Note right of U: "Prediksi revenue bulan depan?"
    
    CONTEXT->>DB: Query historical revenue data
    Note right of DB: SELECT<br/>  SUM(amount) as monthly_revenue,<br/>  DATE_TRUNC('month', paid_at) as month<br/>FROM invoices<br/>WHERE merchant_id = ?<br/>AND paid_at >= NOW() - INTERVAL '6 months'<br/>GROUP BY month<br/>ORDER BY month
    
    DB-->>CONTEXT: Return revenue trend
    Note right of CONTEXT: Data:<br/>Jul: Rp 35M<br/>Aug: Rp 36M<br/>Sep: Rp 37M<br/>Oct: Rp 38M<br/>Nov: Rp 37.5M<br/>Dec: Rp 37.5M (projected)
    
    CONTEXT->>CONTEXT: Calculate trend
    Note right of CONTEXT: Analysis:<br/>- Average growth: +2.5%<br/>- Current occupancy: 92%<br/>- Upcoming contracts: 2 renewal
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: Send with calculations
    
    GEMINI->>GEMINI: Generate forecast
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Return prediction
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Prediksi Revenue Januari 2026:<br/><br/>📈 Estimasi: Rp 38-39 juta<br/><br/>Basis analisis:<br/>- Tren 6 bulan: +2.5% per bulan<br/>- Occupancy rate: 92% (stabil)<br/>- 2 kontrak diperpanjang<br/>- Asumsi: tidak ada tenant keluar<br/><br/>💡 Untuk tingkatkan revenue:<br/>- Isi unit kosong (2 unit)<br/>- Review harga sewa (pasar naik 5%)<br/>- Tawarkan kontrak tahunan<br/><br/>[Lihat Analisis Detail]"
    
    FE->>U: Display forecast with recommendations
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: VENDOR CHATBOT FLOW

    Note over U,CONTEXT: Vendor Business Tips

    U->>FE: Open vendor chatbot
    Note right of U: User role: Vendor
    
    U->>FE: Ask for business advice
    Note right of U: "Tips untuk tingkatkan penjualan?"
    
    CONTEXT->>DB: Query vendor performance
    Note right of DB: Context for Vendor:<br/>- Total orders: 127<br/>- Completion rate: 95%<br/>- Avg rating: 4.7<br/>- Revenue this month: Rp 12.5M<br/>- Top products<br/>- Peak order times<br/>- Customer retention
    
    DB-->>CONTEXT: Return performance data
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: Send with vendor context
    
    GEMINI->>GEMINI: Analyze & generate tips
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Return personalized advice
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Tips tingkatkan penjualan:<br/><br/>✅ Kamu sudah bagus di:<br/>- Rating tinggi (4.7★)<br/>- Completion rate 95%<br/><br/>💡 Peluang improvement:<br/><br/>1. Peak Hours Optimization<br/>   Order paling banyak: 18:00-21:00<br/>   → Tambah kapasitas di jam ini<br/><br/>2. Product Strategy<br/>   Top seller: Cuci Kilat (Rp 15k/kg)<br/>   → Buat paket bundle<br/>   → Promo di slow hours<br/><br/>3. Customer Retention<br/>   Repeat customer: 45%<br/>   → Program loyalty<br/>   → Voucher untuk order ke-5<br/><br/>4. Seasonal Promo<br/>   Akhir bulan = peak demand<br/>   → Diskon 10% untuk pre-order<br/><br/>[Buat Promo] [Lihat Analytics]"
    
    FE->>U: Display actionable tips
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: Conversation History & Context

    FE->>DB: Store conversation
    Note right of DB: INSERT INTO chatbot_history<br/>user_id, role,<br/>conversation_id,<br/>message_pair (user + AI),<br/>context_snapshot,<br/>actions_taken,<br/>timestamp
    
    DB->>DB: Maintain conversation context
    Note right of DB: Keep last 10 message pairs<br/>for context continuity
    
    U->>FE: Continue conversation
    Note right of U: "Gimana cara buat promo?"<br/>(Follow-up question)
    
    CONTEXT->>DB: Load conversation history
    DB-->>CONTEXT: Return previous messages
    
    CONTEXT->>CONTEXT: Build context with history
    Note right of CONTEXT: Include in prompt:<br/>"Previous conversation:<br/>User asked about sales tips.<br/>We recommended creating promos.<br/>Now asking how to create promos.<br/><br/>Guide them through the process."
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: Send with full context
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Return step-by-step guide
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Cara buat promo di SiHuni:<br/><br/>1. Buka Halaman Produk<br/>   Dashboard → Produk → Pilih produk<br/><br/>2. Klik 'Set Promotion'<br/><br/>3. Atur Detail Promo:<br/>   - Harga promo: Rp 12k (dari 15k)<br/>   - Tanggal mulai<br/>   - Tanggal akhir<br/>   - Label: 'Diskon Akhir Bulan'<br/><br/>4. Simpan<br/><br/>💡 Tips:<br/>- Durasi optimal: 3-7 hari<br/>- Diskon efektif: 10-20%<br/>- Promosikan di forum tenant<br/><br/>[Buka Halaman Produk]"
    
    FE->>U: Display with navigation
    
    U->>FE: Click "Buka Halaman Produk"
    FE->>U: Navigate to /vendor/products
    FE->>U: Keep chatbot open (minimized)
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: Error Handling & Fallback

    U->>FE: Ask unclear question
    Note right of U: "Itu gimana ya?"<br/>(Ambiguous reference)
    
    CONTEXT->>GEMINI: Send request
    
    GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: Detect ambiguity
    Note right of GEMINI: Response:<br/>"Maaf, saya kurang paham pertanyaan kamu.<br/><br/>Bisa dijelaskan lebih detail?<br/><br/>Atau pilih topik yang ingin ditanyakan:<br/>🏠 Properti & Unit<br/>👥 Tenant Management<br/>💰 Pembayaran<br/>📊 Laporan<br/>⚙️ Pengaturan"
    
    FE->>U: Display clarification request
    
    alt Gemini API Error
        GEMINI-->>CONTEXT: API Error (timeout/limit)
        
        CONTEXT->>FE: Return fallback response
        Note right of FE: Fallback:<br/>"Maaf, sedang ada gangguan.<br/>Silakan coba lagi atau hubungi<br/>support@sihuni.com"
        
        FE->>DB: Log error for monitoring
    end
    
    Note over U,CONTEXT: Chatbot Analytics

    FE->>DB: Track chatbot metrics
    Note right of DB: Metrics tracked:<br/>- Total conversations<br/>- Messages per session<br/>- Response time<br/>- User satisfaction (thumbs up/down)<br/>- Common questions<br/>- Conversion rate (action taken)<br/>- Error rate<br/>- API costs
    
    DB->>DB: Aggregate for insights
    Note right of DB: Insights for improvement:<br/>- Most asked questions → Add to FAQ<br/>- Low satisfaction → Improve prompts<br/>- High error queries → Train model<br/>- Expensive queries → Optimize context